<p>Dame Cressida said Sgt Ratana was known as a 'big guy' with a 'big heart'. </p>

<p>She said: 'A lovely man, respected by his colleagues, officers, staff and of course by members of the public, including, I may say, suspects arrested or dealt with in custody.</p>

<p>'He was very well known locally and he will be remembered so fondly in Croydon and missed there, as well as in the Met and in the rugby world.'</p>

<p>Dame Cressida said he leaves behind a partner and an adult son from a previous relationship.</p>

